Bring a large pan of water to the boil with @salt{0.5%tsp}. Chop the @Tenderstem® Broccoli{150%g} into thirds widthways. Crumble the @Feta Cheese{100%g} into chunks.

Pop the @Reduced Fat Creme Fraiche{150%g}, @Olive and Caper Tomato Sauce{1%pot} and half the feta into a #saucepan{} and season with @salt{} and @black pepper{}. Cook, stirring, on a medium heat until the feta has melted and the sauce is piping hot, ~{2-3%minutes}. Taste and add more salt and pepper if you like.

Add the broccoli and @Sun-Dried Tomato, Pecorino & Aubergine Cappellacci{1} to the pan of boiling water and cook for ~{4%minutes}. Once cooked, drain in a #colander{} then carefully stir the pasta and broccoli through the sauce, making sure not to break the pasta up. Divide this between plates and top with the remaining feta and @Walnuts{20%g}. Enjoy!